messages.message: Property App\Entity\User::$roles type has no value type specified in iterable type array.
Method App\Entity\User::setRoles() has parameter $roles with no value type specified in iterable type array.
Method App\Entity\User::getPassword() should return string but returns string|null.

PHPDoc tag @implements contains generic type Symfony\Component\Security\Core\User\PasswordUpgraderInterface<App\Entity\User> but interface Symfony\Component\Security\Core\User\PasswordUpgraderInterface is not generic.
